Usage: app [flags]
Flags:
Static help output.
      --name NAME          Service name (default: demo) (env: APP_NAME)
  -p, --port PORT          API port (default: 8080) (env: APP_PORT)
      --mode <dev|prod>    Mode (allowed: dev, prod) (default: dev) (env: APP_MODE)
  -h, --help               Show help
